-- Saudi Arabia Will Have Steel Rebar Supply Shortages, Watan Says
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-02-25T09:54:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-25/saudi-arabia-will-have-steel-rebar-supply-shortages-watan-says.html
Saudi Arabia  will have a shortage of
12-millimeter steel rebar supplies as demand increases from
construction companies,  al-Watan  newspaper reported, citing
unidentified distributors of the product.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
